menu "Picture Frame"

    config TEST_MODE
        bool "Test mode (run diagnostics instead of production boot)"
        default n
        help
            When enabled, app_main() runs the full test suite (PMIC, and
            future driver diagnostics) instead of the normal boot-update-sleep
            cycle.  Enable via 'idf.py menuconfig' or sdkconfig.defaults for
            development and bring-up; leave disabled for production builds.

endmenu
